snippet.title: YARG Setlist: Wave 4 Trailer
snippet.description:
Wave 4 is here! Check out 5 new songs featuring Kidd Judo, Garlagan, Levia, Our Common Collapse, and NyxTheShield available now through the launcher! Just download/update the setlist and the songs will automatically be included in your library when you launch YARG.

If you're a developer, artist, or band and are interested in contributing to YARG, feel free to join us on Discord, GitHub, or contact us via our email. We are 100% open source and always welcome anyone who wants to contribute!

Interested in getting your music added to the official YARG setlist or a DLC pack? Reach out to yargchartingteam@gmail.com and we'll get back to you as soon as possible!
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Website and Download: https://yarg.in/
Discord: https://discord.gg/sqpu4R552r
GitHub: https://github.com/YARC-Official/YARG
